import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.tanh(x1)
    v1 = jnp.sin(x1)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x2, v1)
    v3 = jnp.subtract(x1, v0)
    v4 = jnp.exp(x0)
    v5 = jnp.abs(x1)
    v6 = jnp.abs(x2)
